PrecisAuthority (a) to enter into an AGREEMENT with THE REGIONAL DISTRICT OF FRASER-CHEAM which provides for the transfer to the aforementioned of the lands, premises, equipment and chattels comprising and associated with HOPE AIRPORT in Hope, British Columbia, who shall continue to operate and maintain them as a licensed public airport, and (b) to revoke Order in Council P.C. 1991-16/799 (previous authority to transfer).
